---
title: Bacon & Veggie-Loaded Gnocchi  with Tomato Sugo & Green Hazelnut Salad
description: Soft pillowy bundles of potato gnocchi, smothered in cheese and baked until deliciously golden and oozy. Now, if
that hasn’t got your mouth watering, wait until you reveal this dish of bubbling goodness from underneath the grill.
